hildren":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"16","text":"↑ VCL, VAP (velocidades espermáticas)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"20","parent":"0","text":"Evidencia\\NClínica","guid":"TKOod7KYxct6muJOGs5j2g","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"Vs Gradiente de\\NDensidad (DGC)","guid":"87FW0iUyvQVu3tHFGu6KXQ","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"↑ Motilidad, VAP, ALHD (p<0.01)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"21","text":"↑ Tasa fertilización","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"21","text":"↑ Formación blastocisto","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"21","text":"↑ Blastocistos buena calidad","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"26","parent":"20","text":"Vs Swim-up\\N(IVIRMA Valencia,\\N2025)","guid":"HGI3GBjIORwLtT-aZyQ5Aw","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"SDF ZyMōt 11% vs swim-up 20.3% → diferencia significativa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"26","text":"↑ Blastocistos útiles por oocito fertilizado (ciclos propios)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"26","text":"Beneficio más marcado con OOCITOS PROPIOS (calidad normal)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"26","text":"Sin diferencia significativa con oocitos donados (edad avanzada → menor capacidad reparación ADN)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"31","parent":"20","text":"Vs Centrifugación\\N(Zaha et al., 2023)","guid":"NS1A5MdGQHECGZOXxLho5w","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"Sin diferencia en tasa fertilización (p=0.87)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"31","text":"↑ Tasa blastocisto (p=0.046)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"31","text":"↑ Embarazo clínico (p=0.049)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"35","parent":"0","text":"Aplicación Clínica","guid":"","children":[{"id":"36","parent":"35","text":"INDICACIONES PRINCIPALES","guid":"","children":[{"id":"37","parent":"36","text":"Alta fragmentación ADN (SDF >30% → tu caso: 47%)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"36","text":"Fallo previo FIV/ICSI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"36","text":"Infertilidad idiopática","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"36","text":"Oligoteratozoospermia con SDF elevada","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"41","parent":"35","text":"PROTOCOLO DE USO","guid":"","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"Muestra de semen → chip ZyMōt directamente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"41","text":"Tiempo de migración: ~20-30 min","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"41","text":"Recuperación de espermios en cámara de salida","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"41","text":"Selección directa para ICSI","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"46","parent":"35","text":"LIMITACIONES","guid":"","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"Rendimiento total menor (menos espermios recuperados)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"46","text":"No útil en azoospermia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"46","text":"Beneficio limitado si SDF <15% (no agrega valor sustancial)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"50","parent":"0","text":"Comparativa de Técnicas de Selección","guid":"","children":[{"id":"51","parent":"50","text":"ZyMōt (Microfluidics)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"52","parent":"51","text":"Mecanismo → MOTILIDAD PASIVA","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"51","text":"SDF resultante → ~11%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"51","text":"Sin centrifugación → ↓ estrés oxidativo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"51","text":"Dispositivo → placa/chip","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"56","parent":"50","text":"PICSI (ácido hialurónico)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"57","parent":"56","text":"Mecanismo → unión hialuronato","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"56","text":"Selecciona espermios MADUROS con receptores hialuronato","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"56","text":"Correlación inversa con SDF","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"56","text":"Dispositivo → placa con ácido hialurónico adherido","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"61","parent":"50","text":"MACS (Annexin V Microbeads)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"Mecanismo → SELECCIÓN NEGATIVA por apoptosis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"61","text":"Elimina espermios con fosfatidilserina en membrana externa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"61","text":"Marca de apoptosis/fragmentación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"61","text":"Dispositivo → columna magnética (Miltenyi Biotec)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"66","parent":"50","text":"IMSI","guid":"","children":[{"id":"67","parent":"66","text":"Mecanismo → morfología ultraestructural ×6600","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"66","text":"Identifica vacuolas nucleares","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"66","text":"Selección visual por embriólogo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"66","text":"No mide SDF directamente","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"71","parent":"0","text":"Tu Caso Clínico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"72","parent":"71","text":"SDF 47% → MUY ELEVADA (VR <27%)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"71","text":"Oligoteratozoospermia moderada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"71","text":"Varicocele significativo (causa activa de ↑ ROS)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"71","text":"ICSI + PGT-A planificado con Dr. Sánchez","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"71","text":"ZyMōt → lógica fisiopatológica DIRECTA para tu caso","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"71","text":"CONSIDERAR también","guid":"","children":[{"id":"78","parent":"77","text":"Varicocelectomía pre-ciclo → ↓ causa upstream de SDF","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"77","text":"Antioxidantes oral →  CoQ10, VitC+E, zinc, omega-3, selenio","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"77","text":"Segundo espermiograma post-intervención (3-4 meses)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"81","parent":"0","text":"Perlas Clínicas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"82","parent":"81","text":"ZyMōt = chip o placa → término que usa el laboratorio","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"81","text":"La centrifugación per se AUMENTA el SDF → ZyMōt lo evita","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"81","text":"SDF 47% no se corrige solo con antioxidantes si varicocele sigue activo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"81","text":"Beneficio de ZyMōt mayor con oocitos propios que con donados","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"81","text":"No combinar ZyMōt con centrifugación → pierde la ventaja","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"81","text":"El PGT-A no sustituye la selección espermática → son complementarios","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"81","text":"Preguntar a Dr. Sánchez si usan ZyMōt o variante equivalente (hay otros chips similares como CA0)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"89","parent":"0","text":"VER TAMBIÉN","guid":"","children":[{"id":"90","parent":"89","text":"→ Infertilidad Masculina (Andrología)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"89","text":"→ Varicocele (Andrología)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"92","parent":"0","text":"Referencias","guid":"","children":[{"id":"93","parent":"92","text":"1. Tachibana R, et al. Comparative Evaluation of Two Microfluidic Sperm Sorting Devices. Reprod Med Biol. 2026;25(1):e70010. doi:10.1002/rmb2.70010","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"92","text":"2. Pardiñas ML, et al. Impact of a microfluidic-based selection device on sperm DNA fragmentation and ICSI cycles. F&S Science. 2025;6(4):377-386. doi:10.1016/j.xfss.2025.05.002","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"92","text":"3. Zaha I, et al. Comparative Study of Sperm Selection Techniques for Pregnancy Rates in an Unselected IVF-ICSI Population. J Pers Med. 2023;13(4):619. doi:10.3390/jpm13040619","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"96","parent":"92","text":"4. Agarwal A, et al. Male infertility. The Lancet. 2020. (Guía Drive)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":96,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas/General","filename":"Zymot Seleccion Espermatica iPad","id":"map_896","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"Zymot Seleccion Espermatica iPad"}